sfpsNodeTable.name: sfpsNodeTable
sfpsNodeTable.description: A table of bottom layer protocol addresses and related information of recently or curently active nodes (end-stations). This table replaces the sfpsEndSystemTable.

sfpsNodeTableEntry.name: sfpsNodeTableEntry
sfpsNodeTableEntry.description: Each entry contains information pertaining to recently or currently active nodes.

sfpsNodeTableBaseHash.name: sfpsNodeTableBaseHash
sfpsNodeTableBaseHash.description: A hash of the sfpsNodeTableAddress used to identify the instance.

sfpsNodeTableHashIndex.name: sfpsNodeTableHashIndex
sfpsNodeTableHashIndex.description: A count of the non-unique sfpsNodeTableAddress hashes used to identify the instance.

sfpsNodeTableSwitchType.name: sfpsNodeTableSwitchType
sfpsNodeTableSwitchType.description: The address type of the bottom layer address.

sfpsNodeTablePort.name: sfpsNodeTablePort
sfpsNodeTablePort.description: The port on which the node was discovered.

sfpsNodeTableBaseType.name: sfpsNodeTableBaseType
sfpsNodeTableBaseType.description: The address type of the bottom layer address.

sfpsNodeTableEntryType.name: sfpsNodeTableEntryType
sfpsNodeTableEntryType.description: The type of entry represented. This is determined by the way in which the node was learned.

sfpsNodeTableCallTag.name: sfpsNodeTableCallTag
sfpsNodeTableCallTag.description: The tag, reference number, associated with the packet responsible for the generation of this entry

sfpsNodeTableLastHeard.name: sfpsNodeTableLastHeard
sfpsNodeTableLastHeard.description: The elapsed time since the node for this entry last sourced a packet.

sfpsNodeTableAge.name: sfpsNodeTableAge
sfpsNodeTableAge.description: The elapsed time since this entry was created.

sfpsNodeTableAliasCount.name: sfpsNodeTableAliasCount
sfpsNodeTableAliasCount.description: The number of higher layer protocol addresses learned about this node from the same packet it was discovered from.

sfpsNodeTableVlanCount.name: sfpsNodeTableVlanCount
sfpsNodeTableVlanCount.description: The number of vlans to which this node is mapped.

sfpsAliasTable.name: sfpsAliasTable
sfpsAliasTable.description: A table of upper layer protocol addresses (aliases) and abstract group names related to the bottom layer protocol addresses (nodes) found in the sfpsNodeTable. This table replaces the sfpsEntitiesTable.

sfpsAliasTableEntry.name: sfpsAliasTableEntry
sfpsAliasTableEntry.description: Each entry contains information pertaining to upper layer protocol addresses.

sfpsAliasTableAliasHash.name: sfpsAliasTableAliasHash
sfpsAliasTableAliasHash.description: A hash of the sfpsAliasTableAliasAddress used to identify the instance.

sfpsAliasTableBaseHash.name: sfpsAliasTableBaseHash
sfpsAliasTableBaseHash.description: A hash of the sfpsAliasTableNodeAddress used to identify the instance.

sfpsAliasTableHashIndex.name: sfpsAliasTableHashIndex
sfpsAliasTableHashIndex.description: A count of the non-unique pairs of sfpsAliasTableAliasHash and sfpsAliasTableNodeHash used to identify the instance.

sfpsAliasTableSwitchType.name: sfpsAliasTableSwitchType
sfpsAliasTableSwitchType.description: The address type of the bottom layer address of the switch on which this node was found.

sfpsAliasTableSwitchAddress.name: sfpsAliasTableSwitchAddress
sfpsAliasTableSwitchAddress.description: The bottom layer address value (formatted in printable characters) of the switch on which this node was found.

sfpsAliasTablePort.name: sfpsAliasTablePort
sfpsAliasTablePort.description: The port on which the node was discovered.

sfpsAliasTableBaseType.name: sfpsAliasTableBaseType
sfpsAliasTableBaseType.description: The address type of the bottom layer address of the node.

sfpsAliasTableBaseAddress.name: sfpsAliasTableBaseAddress
sfpsAliasTableBaseAddress.description: The bottom layer address value (formatted in printable characters) of the node.

sfpsAliasTableAliasType.name: sfpsAliasTableAliasType
sfpsAliasTableAliasType.description: The address type of the higher layer address.

sfpsAliasTableAliasAddress.name: sfpsAliasTableAliasAddress
sfpsAliasTableAliasAddress.description: The higher layer address value formatted in printable characters.

sfpsAliasTableAliasAge.name: sfpsAliasTableAliasAge
sfpsAliasTableAliasAge.description: The elapsed time since this alias was discovered and made visible in this table.

sfpsAliasTableSwitchOctets.name: sfpsAliasTableSwitchOctets
sfpsAliasTableSwitchOctets.description: The base address of the switch on which the node associated with this alias entry was found.

sfpsAliasTableBaseOctets.name: sfpsAliasTableBaseOctets
sfpsAliasTableBaseOctets.description: The bottom layer address of the node associated with this alias entry.

sfpsAliasTableAliasOctets.name: sfpsAliasTableAliasOctets
sfpsAliasTableAliasOctets.description: The higher layer address (alias), or the abstract group value.

sfpsAliasTableOpaqueTag.name: sfpsAliasTableOpaqueTag
sfpsAliasTableOpaqueTag.description: An identifier for the type of alias this entry represents.

sfpsAliasTableVlanPolicy.name: sfpsAliasTableVlanPolicy
sfpsAliasTableVlanPolicy.description: The way in which this user was assigned to a vlan. Inherited(2) signifies that the user was assigned its vlan based on the default for its port. Auto-Registered(3) indicates that the user was assigned to its vlan based on packet analysis and vlan manager criteria. Static(4) signifies the user was assigned its vlan by the vlan manager application.

sfpsAliasDeltaTable.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTable
sfpsAliasDeltaTable.description: A table of of newly discovered/lost upper layer protocol addresses (aliases) related to the bottom layer protocol addresses (nodes) found in the sfpsNodeTable.

sfpsAliasDeltaTableEntry.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTableEntry
sfpsAliasDeltaTableEntry.description: Each entry contains information pertaining to a newly discovered or lost upper layer protocol addresses.

sfpsAliasDeltaTableIndex.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTableIndex
sfpsAliasDeltaTableIndex.description: The index into the table. This allows the server to read the information and process it sequentially.

sfpsAliasDeltaTablePort.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTablePort
sfpsAliasDeltaTablePort.description: The port on which the node was discovered.

sfpsAliasDeltaTableBase.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTableBase
sfpsAliasDeltaTableBase.description: The bottom layer address value (MAC) of the node.

sfpsAliasDeltaTableAlias.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTableAlias
sfpsAliasDeltaTableAlias.description: The higher layer address associated with the discovered node.

sfpsAliasDeltaTableAliasLength.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTableAliasLength
sfpsAliasDeltaTableAliasLength.description: The number of alias octets in sfpsAliasDeltaTableAliasOctets.

sfpsAliasDeltaTableOpaqueTag.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTableOpaqueTag
sfpsAliasDeltaTableOpaqueTag.description: A textual identifier for the type of alias this entry represents.

sfpsAliasDeltaTableAliasState.name: sfpsAliasDeltaTableAliasState
sfpsAliasDeltaTableAliasState.description: This enumeration describes the state of the delta table entry. A value of (2) indicates the entry has been added to the alias table. A value of (3) indicates the entry has been deleted from the alias table.

sfpsAliasDeltaCount.name: sfpsAliasDeltaCount
sfpsAliasDeltaCount.description: A count of the number of entries in the alias delta table.

sfpsAliasDeltaSetBack.name: sfpsAliasDeltaSetBack
sfpsAliasDeltaSetBack.description: Used to lock the table so that all the entries may be read without additions or losses. Then after the table has been read the table is unlocked to clear those entries which have been read and allow new entries to be added or lost.
